recipesJson.name: Hazelnut Rum Eggnog
recipesJson.author: DrkRaven1
recipesJson.description: During Hazelnut week I had an idea and with a collaboration with ID1O-T here is so Let's Get Blitzen!: Hazelnut Rum Eggnog. It's the one Classic Holiday Vape you've been waiting for, with baited breath. Here it is in all its glory, with a Divine Hazelnut Flavor that defies the norm. So get ready Captain and raise your foot to the smooth Jamaican Rum...
